{"tid":2027191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太子站外遭警方施加不合法武力 市民入稟向警務處長索償","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T01:48:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8bca31a59fa762351a06900ebe5e6cb37f6ccb","tid":2027191,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/BWAIQB65ZYVKPS67TNUET5C7JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FBWAIQB65ZYVKPS67TNUET5C7JU%2F&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=760e30bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FBWAIQB65ZYVKPS67TNUET5C7JU%2F&h=4b2bfbdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/BWAIQB65ZYVKPS67TNUET5C7JU/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民去年9月22日在太子港鐵站外擺花焚香，紀念疑於8&middot;31在站內遇害的人，並要求政府成立獨立調查委員會。警方當晚清場，並無故向市民及記者施放胡椒噴霧。一名當日在場市民昨入稟區域法院，指警方當晚對他施加不合法武力，導致他受傷，控告代表警務處處長的律政司司長，要求法庭宣佈警方當晚行為違反普通法、基本法及人權法，並須向他賠償。"},{"pid":"f98f47466c3cf6fa9670718a8bbc5a96c82e6df0","tid":2027191,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1102033270306fcf3b7877e1bd09d7e2ac95d561","tid":2027191,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f98f47466c3cf6fa9670718a8bbc5a96c82e6df0","tid":2027191,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=